data.description: Nestled in the Shady River Community, this 4 bedroom home is ready for new homeowners. A large kitchen with granite counters and stainless steel appliances await you.  Enjoy a relaxing moment on the large deck, surrounded by mature trees and overlooking the large backyard and the bayou. There's a big backyard, perfect for outdoor entertaining. This property is close to Sylvan Beach and Kemah Boardwalk and a 30 minute drive to Galveston.
